description: Design mobile bags and cases that better meet the needs and lifestyles of mobile professionals like you. That's the SOLO mission, and it informs every aspect of our business. The SOLO Storm Collection is for those who seek timeless design and proven organization. The SOLO Storm Collection Laptop Backpack features padded sections to hold up to a 16 inch laptop. It also has a universal tablet pocket to hold your iPad tablet or e-Reader. The front has a zip-down organizer, front zippered accessory pockets, and exterior side mesh pockets. It sits comfortably on your shoulders with the padded, adjustable straps, and the sturdy carry handle allows for easy portability. SOLO offers new freedom to create your own work space, any time and any place. Get the satisfaction, comfort and confidence that come with knowing that you've found the "perfect bag" for you.
